OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777568754
OL,3,CThree teens detained for luring man to
OL,4,Chis death in Sheppey
OL,6,FThree teenagers have been detained for
OL,7,Fkilling a man they thought was a
OL,8,Fpaedophile by luring him to a Kent
OL,9,Fbeach before one threw rocks and a
OL,10,Fbottle at him.
OL,12,FA 16-year-old girl and a 16-year-old
OL,13,Fboy were sentenced to seven years in
OL,14,Fcustody, and a 15-year-old boy was
OL,15,Fhanded a five-year term, at the Old
OL,16,FBailey on Thursday for the
OL,17,Fmanslaughter of Alexander Cashford,
OL,18,F49, in Leysdown-on-Sea on the Isle of
OL,19,FSheppey on August 10 last year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
