OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777568754
OL,3,CThree teens detained for luring man to
OL,4,Chis death in Sheppey
OL,6,FThey had been on trial at Woolwich
OL,7,FCrown Court accused of murdering Mr
OL,8,FCashford, but all three teenagers were
OL,9,Facquitted of murder and charged with
OL,10,Fmanslaughter.
OL,12,FSentencing the trio on Thursday, Mrs
OL,13,FJustice Cheema-Grubb said she accepted
OL,14,Fit started out as a "bit of mischief"
OL,15,Fof teenagers on holiday, but turned
OL,16,Finto "dangerous misconduct which
OL,17,Frisked and ultimately took a man's
OL,18,Flife".
OL,26,@vD@UOUvD@eO]xD@FOUzD@EO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
