OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777568754
OL,3,CThree teens detained for luring man to
OL,4,Chis death in Sheppey
OL,6,FJurors were previously told Mr
OL,7,FCashford had given the girl his number
OL,8,Fon August 8, after meeting her by
OL,9,Fchance at an amusement arcade, and
OL,10,Fthat he also handed her a business
OL,11,Fcard with a name on that was not his.
OL,13,FUsing the alias Sienna, the three
OL,14,Fteenagers exchanged messages with Mr
OL,15,FCashford and arranged to meet him by
OL,16,Fthe sea wall in Leysdown.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777568754
OL,3,CThree teens detained for luring man to
OL,4,Chis death in Sheppey
OL,6,FDanny Robinson KC, defending the girl,
OL,7,Ftold the trial that texting Mr
OL,8,FCashford started as a "big laugh", and
OL,9,Fmay have turned "into a desire to
OL,10,Fexpose him as someone who should be
OL,11,Fnamed and shamed".
OL,13,FHowever, the attack was not the
OL,14,Fproduct of an "organised plan to kill
OL,15,For cause anyone really serious harm,
OL,16,Fit was a childish escapade that got
OL,17,Fout of hand very quickly with tragic
OL,18,Fconsequences", he said.
OL,26,@pD@WOUpD@aO]qD@QOUsD@QO]vD@OOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
