OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777568754
OL,3,CThree teens detained for luring man to
OL,4,Chis death in Sheppey
OL,6,FThe girl and the younger male
OL,7,Fdefendant said there was never a plan
OL,8,Fto hit Mr Cashford, the court heard.
OL,10,FMr Cashford met the 16-year-old female
OL,11,Fdefendant at around 7pm on August 10
OL,12,F2025 at the seafront in Leysdown-on-
OL,13,FSea, and just over an hour later he
OL,14,Fwas dead, the court was told.
OL,16,FProsecutors say Mr Cashford was chased
OL,17,Fand hit with rocks and a bottle, and
OL,18,Fwas found lying face down in mud.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777568754
OL,3,CThree teens detained for luring man to
OL,4,Chis death in Sheppey
OL,6,FA post-mortem examination showed he
OL,7,Fhad injuries to his face and head,
OL,8,Fbruises on his limbs and body, and a
OL,9,Fnumber of fractured ribs that had
OL,10,Fpunctured his lung.
OL,12,FDuring the trial, it was heard the
OL,13,Fgirl and the younger male defendant
OL,14,Fsaid there was never a plan to hit Mr
OL,15,FCashford.
OL,17,FAt the sentencing hearing on Thursday,
OL,18,FDanny Robinson KC said the girl has
OL,19,Fthought about what she did wrong and
OL,20,Fin an expert's view she is remorseful
OL,21,Ffor her actions.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777568754
OL,3,CThree teens detained for luring man to
OL,4,Chis death in Sheppey
OL,6,FMeanwhile, for the 15-year-old
OL,7,Fdefendant, barrister Benjamin Newton
OL,8,FKC asked for an intense supervision
OL,9,Forder instead of youth detention for
OL,10,Fthe boy, whom he said "played a minor
OL,11,Frole" in the incident.
OL,13,FMr Newton said the youngest boy, who
OL,14,Fwas 14 at the time, did not arm
OL,15,Fhimself when he had the opportunity to
OL,16,Fdo so and his risk of reoffending is
OL,17,Flow.
OL,26,@rD@WOUsD@EO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
