FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777568754
OL,3,CThree teens detained for luring man to
OL,4,Chis death in Sheppey
OL,6,FA statement from Mr Cashford's
OL,7,Fparents, David and Linda, read out at
OL,8,Fthe sentencing hearing described him
OL,9,Fas a "kind, friendly and compassionate
OL,10,Fperson" who cared about local animals
OL,11,Fand wildlife, and loved all sports.
OL,13,FThey said they were "emotionally
OL,14,Fcrushed" and the impact on the family
OL,15,Fwas "practically impossible to put
OL,16,Finto words".
OL,26,@qD@FOUrD@GO]uD@UOUvD@HO]wD@EOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
